### ? Check Point 4: Verify Price Detail Replicas Created
### Execute SQL:
/*
SELECT 
    pd.id,
    p.name as price_name,
    v.sku as variant_sku,
    pd.unit_price,
    pd.is_active
FROM cart.in_stock_product_price_detail_replicas pd
JOIN cart.in_stock_price_replicas p ON pd.in_stock_price_id = p.id
JOIN cart.in_stock_product_variant_replicas v ON pd.in_stock_product_variant_id = v.id
WHERE v.sku IN ('MF-UCS-STD', 'MF-UCS-BLK')
ORDER BY p.priority DESC, v.sku;

Expected: 3 rows
- MF-UCS-STD with Black Friday: 6799000
- MF-UCS-BLK with Black Friday: 7299000
- MF-UCS-STD with Regular Price: 7999000
*/

